Package kdl.prox.datagen2.structure

Class Summary
SyntheticGraphClusters Creates a cluster graph NOTE: It assumes the database is empty, but initialized!
SyntheticGraphForestFire Createst a ForestFire Graph NOTE: It assumes the database is empty, but initialized!
SyntheticGraphGrid Creates a grid graph, with n nodes and sqrt(n) sides.
SyntheticGraphIID Creates a random graph, with nodes with a degree specified in degreeDistribs or objectSpec There are two types of nodes, S and T.
SyntheticGraphLattice Creates a lattice graph, with n nodes and a given degree for each node.
SyntheticGraphRandom Creates a random graph, with n nodes and e edges NOTE: It assumes the database is empty, but initialized!
SyntheticGraphToroidalLattice Creates a graph as a toroidal lattice with 'side' nodes per size.
